\lim_{n \rightarrow \infty} \sum^n_{k=1} \frac {1} {k+n} = \ln 2
\lim_{n\rightarrow\infty}\sum_{k=1}^{n}\frac{1}{n}\frac{1}{\frac{k}{n}+1}
\int_{0}^{1}\frac{1}{x+1}dx
\gamma
\sum_{k=1}^n\frac{1}{k}=\log n+\gamma+o(1)
\sum_{k=1}^n\frac{1}{k+n}=\sum_{k=n+1}^{2n}\frac{1}{k}=\sum_{k=1}^{2n}\frac{1}{k}-\sum_{k=n}^{2n}\frac{1}{k}=\log(2n)-\log(n)+o(1)=\log 2+o(1)
